data.description: VA ASSUMABLE MORTGAGE AT 2.75% for a qualified VA buyer. MOTIVATED SELLER! MAKE AN OFFER! This stunning newly remodeled 3-bedroom + Large first floor Den/Bedroom, 3-bathroom dream house is a masterpiece of modern design and comfort, offering an unparalleled lifestyle experience. Upon entering this exquisite home, you'll immediately notice the open and airy layout.  The heart of this home is the chef's kitchen, boasting top-of-the-line stainless steel appliances, granite countertops, and a spacious breakfast bar.   The Large first floor Den can be used as a fourth bedroom. The master suite is particularly impressive, featuring a walk-in closet and a luxurious en-suite bathroom with a double vanity, and a separate shower. The additional two bedrooms share two impeccably designed bathrooms, all finished with high-quality fixtures and finishes.  Valencia Country Club is a gated community in a growing area, where you can enjoy the public 18-hole golf course & putting green, resort-style pool & clubhouse, fitness center and much more. The newly constructed Big Corkscrew Island Regional Park, Founders Square, Mercato are a short drive away. HOA fees are one of the lowest in the area.
